CIE Systems Inc, a unit of C.Itoh Electronics Inc, said it established a program to providelease and lease-purchase financing for buyers of its businesscomputer systems and electronic products.    The program will be administered by CFC Leasing, anindependent company, and more than 100 mln dlrs in funds areexpected to be available over the next four years from aconsortium of six financial institutions, the company said.    C. Itoh Electronics Inc is a U.S. unit of (C. Itoh and CoLtd) of Japan. Reuter&#3;